<div class="title">Everybody's Favorite Crutch</div>
<div class="substance">Caffeine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=mapk33&Exact=1">mapk33</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; mapk33. "Everybody's Favorite Crutch: An Experience with Caffeine (exp8167)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 29, 2003. erowid.org/exp/8167</div>

<br/>



